scenes.description: Mori Calliope enters a hub world of memories and visits 'Smol Ina's' room, reminiscing about the original VRChat locations.
Calli returns to the hub, sees the crying Yagoo statue, and enters her own old room, the 'Mori Cave'.
She visits 'KFP Square', remembering the various events and games held there like egg hunts.
Calli explores the Atlantis-themed room belonging to Gura and thanks the creators Seafoam and Malin.
She visits the 'Open Bar', a frequent hangout spot for the HoloMyth members in their early days.
Calli visits the HoloMyth First Anniversary stage and becomes emotional reflecting on their growth.
Finally, she visits the Sunfish Ship, recalling adventures and seeing the 'big' Sana.
